<p><strong>What to do with the data:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Posts not getting indexed?</strong> Check your <a href="/blog/on-page-seo-guide/">on-page SEO</a>. Missing meta tags, thin content, or crawl errors keep pages out of Google's index.</li>
<li><strong>Low click-through rate?</strong> Rewrite the title and meta description. A/B test different formats.</li>
<li><strong>High bounce rate?</strong> The content may not match the search intent. Revisit the keyword and adjust the article angle.</li>
<li><strong>Rankings plateaued?</strong> Add internal links from higher-authority pages. Update the post with fresh data.</li>
</ul>
